## Deployment (Gunicorn + Nginx)

```bash
# Install gunicorn
pip install gunicorn

# Run with gunicorn
gunicorn -w 4 -b 0.0.0.0:8000 "app:create_app()"

# Production config
gunicorn -w 4 \
  --bind unix:/tmp/flask.sock \
  --access-logfile logs/access.log \
  --error-logfile logs/error.log \
  "app:create_app('production')"
```
